sequenceDiagram
    participant iPad as iPad (Blink + Tailscale)
    participant DERP as Tailscale Coordination<br/>(or direct P2P)
    participant TS as Pod Tailscale Sidecar
    participant SSHD as Pod sshd :22

    iPad->>DERP: Connect to workspace-1 (100.x.x.1)
    DERP->>TS: Encrypted WireGuard tunnel
    Note over DERP: Traffic is E2E encrypted<br/>DERP only relays if no direct path
    TS->>SSHD: Forward to localhost:22
    SSHD-->>iPad: SSH session (zsh + Rust + Claude Code)
